Directory Notes - neat little system

Features:
    display contents of .notes file in current directory if they exist
    display overview of directories with notes (ls)
    display multiple .notes if provided on the command line
    automatically remove .notes dirs when they are deleted
    delete unwanted .notes
    built-in test

